{"tid":1575620,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"係咪一定要FC? FC 來做咩?","createTime":"2019-09-17T02:08:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-17T02:47:05.000Z","uid":157353,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8bfe6a70c2202a24fc4ad157c41c7b2da9361f51","tid":1575620,"uid":157353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T02:08:40.000Z","msg":"FC 來做咩?<br />\nFC 係唔想炒車,<br />\n如果一定冇証據証明炒車, FC 來做咩?<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">太子, 新屋嶺會唔會有人提出有說服力証據?</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n唔洗FC 前提下, <br />\n新屋嶺係警察做定公安做邊樣返應大D?<br />\n太子有死定冇死邊樣返應大D?<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>如果一定冇後果但係都要FC咁公道, 而加做咩獅鳥???</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n我相信大家會學習, 呢個post 唔係要求大家點做, 係想大家諗下同埋預言將來大家取態"},{"pid":"e71ad81729d77dceee804e98a7981461d4d9cf6b","tid":1575620,"uid":256131,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T02:10:35.000Z","msg":"見住一堆fc撚係唔係都問人有冇fc就憫<br />\n明知冇得fc fc黎把撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3795b4f092d451a95366645037aad9f8a5dd910b","tid":1575620,"uid":157353,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T02:10:49.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">當成事實來文宣其實唔係問題</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"312b1764edfa4cec213bcd5c007f8f733ef62c86","tid":1575620,"uid":274161,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T02:14:40.000Z","msg":"陰謀論無辦法FC（也無需FC），但前提在於陰謀論裏面的每個論據都真實（需要FC）<br />\n<br />\n新聞如果有source，比如上次警方掉汽油彈的視頻就需要FC，因爲呢d證據太明顯，如果不FC就有位畀人入"},{"pid":"1ceda7f9590143848a3e65e512cc675a739a57f8","tid":1575620,"uid":263822,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T02:15:06.000Z","msg":"科學精神<br />\n假說係需要<br />\n但求證同樣重要"},{"pid":"07f319e365656ae9e2e146dc66a187e432af2da2","tid":1575620,"uid":157353,"like":0,"dis